### Test 404
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:8080/quizzes/999


### =========================================
### DELETE NON EXISTING QUIZ
### Test 404 przy delete
### =========================================
DELETE http://localhost:8080/quizzes/999


### =========================================
### UPDATE NON EXISTING QUIZ
### Test 404 przy update
### =========================================
PUT http://localhost:8080/quizzes/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Does Not Exist",
  "questions": []
}
